abstract: Gunman shoots and wounds Saudi preacher and diplomat Aaidh al-Qarni before being killed by police officer in Zamboanga, Philippines.
lead_paragraph: A gunman attacked and wounded a Saudi preacher and a diplomat from Saudi Arabia’s embassy late Tuesday before being killed by a police officer.

headline.main: The Philippines: Gunman Wounds Saudi Preacher and Embassy Worker
headline.print_headline: Asia; The Philippines: Gunman Wounds Saudi Preacher and Embassy Worker
